{"type": "article", "id": 27181, "title": "小鱼刀", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-23T06:53:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132414GXusPefbgtI4zwr0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这一系列外形可爱的小鱼刀由设计师 Axel Brechensbauer 为 Areaware 设计，其中“鱼身”是由山毛榉制成的刀柄，刀片可以通过设计成鱼鳍的拉钩取出，“鱼尾”则是一个开瓶器。三条“小鱼”成套出售的价格为 65 美元，你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.areaware.com/collections/bundles/products/fish-pocket-knife-bundle\">链接</a>购买。试想一下，当你和朋友在公园野餐，你从口袋中掏出一条“小鱼”，用它轻松地开启一罐啤酒或是切开一个水果，会是多么吸引眼球的一件事。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132412EC23c6P14tie9kG0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132412E3jug1sfKpG5HRIq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132413dOG3WoCp8iVZTEez.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132413FPbBmcnCwKlzsDTo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}